prodNameC: 羅氏可霸斯免疫分析人類絨毛膜促素性腺激素+β次單位檢驗試劑
ingredientsDesc:
Reagents - working solutions
M   Streptavidin-coated microparticles (transparent cap), 1 bottle, 6.5 mL: Streptavidin-coated microparticles 0.72 mg/mL; preservative.
R1  Anti-hCG-Ab~biotin (gray cap), 1 bottle, 9 mL: Biotinylated monoclonal anti-hCG antibodies (mouse) 2.6 mg/L; phosphate buffer 40 mmol/L, pH 7.5; preservative.
R2  Anti-hCG-Ab~Ru(bpy)   (black cap), 1 bottle, 10 mL: Monoclonal anti-hCG antibody (mouse) labeled with ruthenium complex 4.6 mg/L; phosphate buffer 40 mmol/L, pH 6.5; preservative.

CalSet - working solutions
• HCG+β Cal1: 2 bottles, each for 1.0 mL of calibrator 1
• HCG+β Cal2: 2 bottles, each for 1.0 mL of calibrator 2
Human chorionic gonadotropin (from urine) in two concentration ranges (approx. 1.5 mIU/mL and approx. 2000 mIU/mL) in a buffered human serum matrix.
applicantName: 台灣羅氏醫療診斷設備股份有限公司
applicantAddr: 台北市中山區民權東路3段2號10樓
efficacy: 用於體外定量檢測人類血清及血漿中人類絨毛膜促性腺激素(hCG)加上hCG β-次單元的總量之免疫分析法。Elecsys HCG + β CalSet係用於Elecsys和cobas e免疫分析儀上, 以校正Elecsys HCG + β的定量分析法之校正液組。
